sequenceDiagram
    participant Student as Frontend (Student)
    participant GW as API Gateway
    participant PAY as Payment Service
    participant RZP as Razorpay API
    participant RMQ as RabbitMQ
    participant ENR as Enrollment Service
    participant NOT as Notification Service

    Student->>GW: POST /api/payments (Course ID)
    GW->>PAY: Forward Request
    PAY->>RZP: Create Order
    RZP-->>PAY: Order ID
    PAY-->>Student: Razorpay Details
    
    Student->>RZP: Complete Payment UI
    RZP-->>Student: Payment Success (Signature)
    
    Student->>GW: POST /api/payments/verify
    GW->>PAY: Verify Signature
    PAY->>RZP: Fetch Payment Details
    RZP-->>PAY: Confirmed
    PAY->>PAY: Save Transaction (DB)
    PAY->>RMQ: Publish "PAYMENT_SUCCESS" Event
    PAY-->>Student: Success Response

    RMQ-->>ENR: Consume Payment Event
    ENR->>ENR: Create Enrollment (DB)
    ENR->>RMQ: Publish "COURSE_ENROLLED" Event
    
    RMQ-->>NOT: Consume Enrollment Event
    NOT->>NOT: Send Confirmation Email (Mailhog)
    NOT->>NOT: Push WebSocket Notification
